<plot>"Made in Brooklyn" is a seamless story compilation comprised of four short films. The picture captures the essence of Brooklyn, its people, hangouts, smells, life, irony and the comedy of a bunch of "wise guys." The four stories making up "Made in Brooklyn" are entitled "Happy Birthday, Joe," "Wood," "Let it Go!," and "Choose Life." All of the stories are being shot on location in NYC, Brooklyn and upstate NY.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?350906</url></doc>
